{"tid":2423592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年管有士巴拿及索帶罪成 羅德泉下令還押候判","createTime":"2021-02-26T03:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T16:23:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"203e51856622e599396b5f6d1913edf7e4cd935e","tid":2423592,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:56:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13975&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=7bf19f2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13975</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#羅德泉主任裁判官<br />\n#提堂 <br />\n#1201旺角 <br />\n<br />\n胡(19)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n管有適合作非法用途的工具或攻擊性武器並意圖作非法用途使用<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n被控於19年12月1日，在旺角新填地街近山東街交界，管有一支士巴拿及100條索帶<br />\n<br />\n‼️被告認罪‼️<br />\n<br />\n法庭要求索取感化、社會服務令、勞教中心、更生中心和教導所報告。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至3月19日在東區裁判法院判刑，期間還押候判‼️<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"e0bff5198a3353e0afa433b3549649af7f8140b3","tid":2423592,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3bda62437a9429ec1a8f9f1c914f657a36d608","tid":2423592,"uid":87985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"東區判係因為羅官調？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3439ccddf6098943a8002f3c1385660d25c8c6e","tid":2423592,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b3e5ccc1bc2563c176b5462c